ld require destructive or cross-workspace actions.\n\n## Final Output Contract\nReturn a JSON object matching runtime/arckit-runtime/schemas/runtime-result.schema.json. Do not wrap it in Markdown.\n\n## Runtime Options\n- max_rounds: 1\n- adapter: codex-app-server","text_elements":[]}]},"threadId":"019f3da8-d7da-74c2-855a-d493b173a274","turnId":"019f3da8-d809-7402-89ce-bda6ac7a4e03","startedAtMs":1783445903374}}}
